Gio's Movie files: MAIN

Movies MAIN file

MASTER BASE File of Movies [brambles]MyDocs/mov/main.html
This file is copyright 1987, 1989,1990,1993, 1996, 1998 by Gio Wiederhold.
about 15,000 movies, , by about 2800 directors
(20, 034 paragraphs Nov.1998 )
See Remakes.html for relationships among movie contents

Format

Major sections (H2)
  1. HITCHCOCK movies
  2. Other Movies
  3. Miscellaneous, as alternate titles
Minor Sections (H3 year:)
One per year
A table per director starting that year (TABLE, CAPTION)

  1. film
  2. T:title
  3. year
  4. Director (main director only)
  5. P:producers in people, PN: producer name, PU:unknown, PZ:approx.spelling.
  6. S studio in studios, St: studio name, SU:unknown, SD:distributor if different, SL:country/city, SU:unknown.
  7. Process code {bws, bnw, col, \colprocess, cld}, if prc not set.
  8. Category code {BioP, Disa (disaster), Dram, CnR, Comd, Faml, Hist, Horr, Musc, Noir, Romt, ScFi, Susp}, if Ctxx not set.
  9. Awards, if aw not set.
  10. Locale hierarchy; other locale; T(time)
  11. Notes
      in Notes field
    • Alt(T:Alternate title; reason) - there can be more than one.
    • B(Original author of book or play: title)
    • CoD(CoDirector)
    • W(screenwriter)
    • C(Cinematographer)
    • G(ChoreoGrapher)
    • M(Music or Music director: piece)
    • E(editor)
    • V(art, visual effects director)
    • FilmedAt(Locale)
    • Sy(Symbology, mainly for Hitchcock)
    • Lang(language code)
    • Ser(Series name; number)
    • Le(Length of movie: h:m,r) or (Short)
    • R(Rating)
    • Cost(of movie)
    • Inc(Income of Movie)
    • Nt(general)
    • Seen(ddMmmyyyy)
    • VT , VTN(have on videotape) -personal information
